overview:
Moving Company Davie is an operated company with more than four generations of moving experience. We make the moving experience different from start to finish in any kind of relocating process. Our services include quilt-pad wrapping of your furniture, assembly and disassembly as well. Providing high quality moving services to each and every client at affordable rates is our mission. You can take advantage of our pristine storage and moving services, as we provide customized services for our customer’s distinctive and unique move.

We are a full service moving company offering: •Household Moving •Residential Moving •Commercial Moving •Office Moving •Corporate Moving •Relocation moving •Local Moving •Interstate Moving •State to State Moving •Cross Country Moving •Long Distance Moving •National Moving •International Moving

Moving is not an easy task to accomplish; the careful packing, the timing, the lifting of heavy furniture, ensuring your possessions arrive safely to your new locations and the unpacking. With the help of our movers, you can rest assured that we will provide you with a flawless move from start to finish. We’ll take the stress away from you so all you have to do is sit back, relax and enjoy the moving experience.

From the first estimate, we work with your budget and schedule to go beyond your expectations. There is a reason why customers keep coming back to us for their moving needs. Our reputation as movers goes far beyond the Florida area and we’ve worked with people nationwide and even made the most difficult moves easy.
